2
00:01:43,650 --> 00:01:45,140
Shoot!

3
00:01:49,630 --> 00:01:51,790
There's not even a scratch on them!

4
00:01:51,790 --> 00:01:54,100
What's wrong with them?!

5
00:01:55,020 --> 00:01:56,440
Sanji!

6
00:01:56,860 --> 00:02:00,400
Take the injured guy
and get off of this island already.

7
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:03,140
We don't need you here!

8
00:02:03,140 --> 00:02:04,990
They set us up.

9
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:07,240
We'll make them pay!

10
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:12,860
This whole island is Germa 66's target, Sanji!

11
00:02:12,860 --> 00:02:14,260
You guys!

12
00:02:14,770 --> 00:02:18,340
Are they really modified humans
with iron skins?!

13
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:19,970
Bring me a bazooka!

14
00:02:23,650 --> 00:02:26,280
Germa!

15
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:30,610
I thought that you were all dead!
How did you survive?!

16
00:02:30,610 --> 00:02:31,580
What do you mean?

17
00:02:31,580 --> 00:02:37,910
Ten thousand soldiers led by Nusstorte
took down your kingdom!

18
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:41,540
Yeah, some flies swarmed around us,

19
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:43,990
but we swatted
and dumped them in the sea.

20
00:02:43,990 --> 00:02:45,090
What?!

21
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:49,770
Th-This is Mont d'Or! Answer me!

22
00:02:49,770 --> 00:02:53,270
Big Brother Nusstorte! Please answer!

23
00:02:53,270 --> 00:02:57,470
Big Brother Basskarte!
Big Brother Dosmarche!

24
00:02:57,470 --> 00:03:00,950
If anyone's there... answer me!

25
00:03:00,950 --> 00:03:04,700
Just as I feared, it's a series
of unexpected happenings,

26
00:03:04,700 --> 00:03:07,960
to include Pekoms' betrayal-vous plaît !

27
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:14,040
Why did Germa's fleet
appear at Cacao Island-noir ?!

28
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:18,920
What were you halfwits
going to do with our technology?

29
00:03:18,920 --> 00:03:21,360
You couldn't do a thing with it!

30
00:03:22,530 --> 00:03:25,510
You bastards!

31
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:28,130
Sanji! Hurry and go!

32
00:03:28,130 --> 00:03:29,140
Yeah!

33
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:34,530
Snack and the others are
under assault by Germa!

34
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:36,520
Shouldn't we help them?!

35
00:03:36,520 --> 00:03:41,710
Don't get distracted by that!
We've gotta focus on Straw Hat's ship!

36
00:03:42,170 --> 00:03:44,810
Tell that to all ships around the island!

37
00:03:44,810 --> 00:03:45,900
Yes, ma'am!

38
00:03:48,020 --> 00:03:52,840
Mont d'Or and everyone else...
Germa must've outsmarted them!

39
00:03:52,840 --> 00:03:55,440
You were outsmarted too, Brother Daifuku.

40
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:59,770
Tch! But I fought hard to catch up to you!

41
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:04,460
Peanuts Town
Nuts Island

42
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:07,620
Mama's hunger tantrum hasn't stopped yet!

43
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:12,940
We live in an emperor's territory where we're supposed
to be protected in exchange for our lifespan.

44
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:16,310
I can't believe the queen
destroyed this place.

45
00:04:16,310 --> 00:04:19,570
There's no way to remake the wedding cake

46
00:04:16,550 --> 00:04:22,570
Beany-Bean Town
Munchie Island

47
00:04:19,570 --> 00:04:24,700
that the famous Master Streusen took days to bake!

48
00:04:24,700 --> 00:04:30,620
Even Madam Pudding won't be able to
remake it in a mere several hours.

49
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:34,370
The cake Mama craves...

50
00:04:30,750 --> 00:04:34,370
Table Town
Cutlery Island

51
00:04:34,370 --> 00:04:36,060
That's impossible!

52
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:38,380
We should prepare to evacuate!

53
00:04:38,630 --> 00:04:44,130
Sherbet Town
Ice Cream Island

54
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:45,870
Let's get out of here before Mama arrives!

55
00:04:45,870 --> 00:04:47,780
Where is Mama right now?!

56
00:04:47,780 --> 00:04:49,150
On Puffs Island!

57
00:04:49,150 --> 00:04:52,520
It's governed by the
minister of puffs, Madam Chiffon...

58
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:55,720
The hungry Mama is coming to this island!

59
00:04:53,140 --> 00:04:57,400
Puffs Island

60
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,400
Nothing will stop her!

61
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,080
Madam Chiffon...

62
00:04:59,080 --> 00:05:02,360
Why did she bring the cake here?!

63
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:04,980
Run!

64
00:05:11,490 --> 00:05:13,590
Hey, Jinbe!

65
00:05:13,590 --> 00:05:19,140
What do you think about Germa?
Are they friends or foes?

66
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:23,730
They could've escaped already.
Why choose now to help us out?

67
00:05:23,730 --> 00:05:29,480
But... it's just for now that they're helping us, right?
So, how can we trust them?!

68
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:32,650
Oh! Maybe Reiju-san came
to show me her panties...

69
00:05:41,010 --> 00:05:42,620
Hey, can you hear me?!

70
00:05:42,620 --> 00:05:46,790
Sanji! This is the closest
we can get to the island!

71
00:05:46,790 --> 00:05:50,580
I know!
Sail by the harbor at full speed!

72
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:53,480
I'll get there while you're passing by!

73
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:55,130
Sanji-kun ! How's Luffy?!

74
00:05:55,150 --> 00:06:00,010
I got him! I don't have time to talk now!
I'm counting on you, Nami-san !

75
00:06:00,010 --> 00:06:00,970
Okay!

76
00:06:03,620 --> 00:06:05,970
Let's go, Jinbe! To starboard!

77
00:06:05,970 --> 00:06:08,100
To starboard!

78
00:06:09,690 --> 00:06:11,740
Sanji!

79
00:06:11,740 --> 00:06:14,280
You can do it!

80
00:06:23,390 --> 00:06:25,780
Crush Germa!

81
00:06:25,780 --> 00:06:28,300
Where did Black Leg go?!

82
00:06:30,870 --> 00:06:32,750
I can't see because of the dust!

83
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:48,370
There he is!

84
00:06:53,400 --> 00:06:55,060
Shoot him!

85
00:07:04,570 --> 00:07:06,990
Don't let him get away!

86
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:14,580
That's right...
We cannot let him get away, no matter what!

87
00:07:15,790 --> 00:07:20,090
Straw Hat Luffy is...
the one person we cannot forgive!

88
00:07:24,750 --> 00:07:30,640
He didn't escape from Big Brother Katakuri
using dirty tricks...

89
00:07:31,380 --> 00:07:32,690
Big Sister Brûlée?!

90
00:07:33,330 --> 00:07:38,400
Do you wanna know
what really happened in the Mirro-world?

91
00:07:41,380 --> 00:07:43,000
Perfect!

92
00:07:43,000 --> 00:07:47,270
The strongest and best in the world!

93
00:07:48,050 --> 00:07:51,540
Our big brother, Katakuri...

94
00:07:55,210 --> 00:07:57,840
Big Brother...

95
00:08:05,490 --> 00:08:11,920
lost to Straw Hat Luffy!

96
00:08:24,450 --> 00:08:25,830
What?!

97
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:29,960
Katakuri...

98
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,250
Your legendary undefeated record...

99
00:08:33,090 --> 00:08:36,060
was broken by that pipsqueak?

100
00:08:37,720 --> 00:08:41,850
No way!

101
00:08:42,310 --> 00:08:44,680
There's no way our brother would lose!

102
00:08:44,680 --> 00:08:48,020
Commander Katakuri cannot be defeated!

103
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:53,770
He must've used some kind of dirty trick!
That's unforgivable!

104
00:08:58,810 --> 00:09:01,900
Fill him with lead!

105
00:09:05,990 --> 00:09:08,740
Cut him into pieces!

106
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:18,220
Smash Straw Hat Luffy to dust!

107
00:09:18,220 --> 00:09:20,090
Yeah!

108
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:40,280
We won't let you escape, Straw Hat!

109
00:09:58,170 --> 00:10:00,220
Damn you!

110
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:04,050
Straw Hat!

111
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,480
I won't forgive you!

112
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:13,350
